Package: libhpp-util-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libhpp-util0.4c (= ${binary:Version}),
	       libboost-dev (>= 1.35),
	       libboost-filesystem-dev (>= 1.35),
	       libboost-system-dev (>= 1.35),
	       ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for the hpp-util library
 The hpp-util library contains technicals tools for the humanoid path
 planner project.
 .
 It provides an unified error reporting and logging mechanism
 for developers and can also be used to realize benchmarks of
 specific parts of a program.
 .
 This package contains development files (headers and
 shared library symbolic link).

