Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Debugging tools for the Humanoid Path Planner project
 The hpp-util library contains technicals tools for the humanoid path
 planner project.
 .
 It provides an unified error reporting and logging mechanism
 for developers and can also be used to realize benchmarks of
